    {
      "id": "optimistic_7_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "optimistic_7",
      "description": "Looking for a dependable daily driver at a great value? This vehicle is in fair condition and ready for its next adventure! While it shows some honest wear from its time on the road, it remains a functional and spirited ride that\u2019s perfect for someone who appreciates a car with character and potential.",
